", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 248}, {\"ngram\": \"PRNewswire/ --Stone Ridge Schoolof\", \"from\": 263, \"to\": 297}, {\"ngram\": \"the Sacred Heart\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 314}, {\"ngram\": \"an all-girls 1-12 school inBethesda\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 351}, {\"ngram\": \"andErin Gemmell\\u02bc23\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 422}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Representing 15% of the 2024 U.S. Olympic Women's Swimming Team, all three renowned Stone Ridge \\\"Gators\\\" graduated from the independent all-girls school inBethesda, Maryland.\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 661, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 652, \"end\": 660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryland\", \"score\": 0.9967486641644118, \"rank\": 0.0029393923166348896, \"text\": \"Maryland\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"15%\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 503}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 U.S. Olympic Women's Swimming Team\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 550}, {\"ngram\": \"the independent all-girls school inBethesda\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While not uncommon for swimmers from the same college to be named to an Olympic Team together, it is nearly unheard of for three athletes from the same high school to achieve this feat.\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 847, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 693}, {\"ngram\": \"the same college\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic Team\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 746}, {\"ngram\": \"three athletes\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"the same high school\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 825}, {\"ngram\": \"this feat\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 846}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We at Stone Ridge are incredibly proud of these athletes, not only for what they accomplish in the sport of swimming, but for the values and character they represent,\\\" said Head of SchoolCatherine Ronan Karrels'86.\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 1064, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Stone Ridge\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 867}, {\"ngram\": \"these athletes\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 906}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 954}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 966}, {\"ngram\": \"the values\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"character\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"Head\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"SchoolCatherine Ronan\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1052}, {\"ngram\": \"Karrels'86\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our school community has watched these young women train for many years, consistently inspired by their dedication to hitting their goals in the pool while achieving high standards in their academics and other pursuits.\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our school community\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1086}, {\"ngram\": \"these young women\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"many years\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1137}, {\"ngram\": \"their dedication\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1180}, {\"ngram\": \"their goals\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1203}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1215}, {\"ngram\": \"high standards\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1246}, {\"ngram\": \"their academics\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1265}, {\"ngram\": \"other pursuits\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While swimmers strive for their personal best, each one of these champion athletes is also fully dedicated to the concept of team and community - a true lesson on the payoff of consistent hard work, discipline, and practice.\\\"\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1511, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1300}, {\"ngram\": \"these champion athletes\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1368}, {\"ngram\": \"the concept\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"team\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1415}, {\"ngram\": \"community\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"a true lesson\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"the payoff\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1459}, {\"ngram\": \"consistent hard work\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1483}, {\"ngram\": \"discipline\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1495}, {\"ngram\": \"practice\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1509}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stone Ridge Schoolof the Sacred Heart endeavors to develop empowered leaders who serve with faith, intellect, and confidence.\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1638, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1513, \"end\": 1524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Ridge,_New_York\", \"score\": 0.9429892133255964, \"rank\": 0.05718954248365827, \"text\": \"Stone Ridge\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Ridge,_New_York\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Ridge,_New_York\"}, {\"begin\": 1538, \"end\": 1550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Society_of_the_Sacred_Heart\", \"score\": 0.9997588080199442, \"rank\": 0.00024055597557289543, \"text\": \"Sacred Heart\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Society_of_the_Sacred_Heart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Society_of_the_Sacred_Heart\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"empowered leaders\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1589}, {\"ngram\": \"faith\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1610}, {\"ngram\": \"intellect\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1621}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The school is part of a 200-year-old international network of Sacred Heart schools sponsored by the Religious of the Sacred Heart, with origins inFrance.\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1701, \"end\": 1713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Society_of_the_Sacred_Heart\", \"score\": 0.9997588080199442, \"rank\": 0.00024055597557289543, \"text\": \"Sacred Heart\", \"types\": []